{"tid":806773,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG新gp] 絲打減肥共勉group","createTime":"2018-09-05T03:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T07:42:36.000Z","uid":90290,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"490ca76d317d47ae6ebafbd47d56d0403606f0ce","tid":806773,"uid":90290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"減肥對女人泥講係終生事業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但針唔拮到肉其實又冇乜動力減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想開個gp大家鼓勵下篤促下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 18歲以上 (太細減肥影響發育<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 50KG以上 (40幾公斤體脂冇25%你話自己肥既走開啦)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你有明確既減磅目標<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有心理準備有恆心要忍口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我希望呢個group大家會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分享你既減肥方法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日影低分享你既三餐同做左咩運動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 互相比壓力大家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有機會可以一齊做運動<br />\n<br />\n最後最重要一樣野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">減肥係以健康為目的，要搵到適合自己既方法，切勿過度減肥</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdedf9252fac5af12185a86b323432ef58c4f99","tid":806773,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"如果單純想分享下減肥心得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b53f3617f15ccd4b9a4a02dc5d6023bbb66369","tid"